        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "Esposito was in contact with a corrupt man-on-the-inside with a fair amount of control over Future*Tech's autonomous vehicle system. Gerard Little.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 0
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 1,
            "statement": "Gerard Little was able to use autnomous vehicles to store and transport illicit goods safely and inconspicuously.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 1
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "The Esposito operation was so successful at moving goods into the city in great quantity that they became something akin to a wholesale distributor to other crime families.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 1,
            "statement": "Lastly, transactions were dealt in digital currency.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 2
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 1,
            "statement": "Even if what we found was only a fraction of they were making, the amount of money is substantial.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "These are solid conclusions.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": -1
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "Taking these factors into account, we should be able to stop this operation in its tracks.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "However, we came to a realization after your preliminary investigation.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "What exactly did you find out?",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "We put our forensics divison on the case and they found some inconsistencies.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "We cross referenced the financial transaction records, and the numbers don't all match up.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 3
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "Not only that, when we did chemical analysis of the content of some of the bags, the concentrations were off.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": 4
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 1,
            "statement": "Aha, I think I get it.",
            "action": [
                {
                    "type": "propAction",
                    "target": -1
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "Gerard Little was skimming from Esposito's profits, wasn't he?",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "That's what it looks like. Fudging the numbers and mixing placebo into the product allowed him to pocket the extra.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 1,
            "statement": "I guess that explains why Freddie Silva was caught dealing powedered sugar.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 0,
            "statement": "I'd imagine Esposito would not take kindly to this if he found out.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "Given the current circumstances, I would assume that he did in fact find out.",
            "action": [
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "dialogue",
            "speaker": 2,
            "statement": "In any case, keep this potential motive in mind and continue the investigation.",
            "action": [
            ]
        }
